{"tid":1395972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔友入，有關8月5日罷工集會地點","createTime":"2019-08-02T02:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T04:45:49.000Z","uid":193209,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"00d85cb57d6b5d2117e91eea739615d6b8f7982c","tid":1395972,"uid":193209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pieMbtY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpieMbtY.png&h=d4333ebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8rUwnCk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8rUwnCk.png&h=bc75f20b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n發現有兩個問題<br />\n第一，我見其他區全部都係公眾地方<br />\n大埔就係廣福球場<br />\n個廣福場係人造草場，有巴打check咗要book場的<br />\n同時康民署應該唔會批集會用<br />\n我之前專登去睇真係有鎖<br />\n搵咗好耐都搵唔到邊個發起<br />\n問唔到其實係咪有book到場<br />\n最怕到時大家入唔到唔知點算<br />\n如果真係入唔到，其實會唔會轉場(風水球場?)好啲？<br />\n第二個問題係，圖寫嘅係廣福球場<br />\n但細圖背景係廣福公園足球場（有看台）<br />\n呢個好似都要book場的<br />\n我估係整圖嘅巴打搵錯圖<br />\n但搞清楚好啲<br />\n睇下有無人識搞手問清楚好啲<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無柒咗，柒咗就唔洗理我了<br />\n只係驚大家到時混亂"},{"pid":"661409ec5af6e8053f66d08582646ae8c1c59ed5","tid":1395972,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:44:39.000Z","msg":"大元村個公園咪得囉<br />\n<br />\n夠晒大"},{"pid":"1911f138244e46dd29d43714d36262beb3f05c17","tid":1395972,"uid":193209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:44:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kF2mKXd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkF2mKXd.png&h=6e8d84a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廣福球場，無看台<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sRYQDhr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsRYQDhr.png&h=5186d890&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廣福公園足球場，有看台的"},{"pid":"cecd8a655146c2ac0d658de605b4757d807c711c","tid":1395972,"uid":193209,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"661409ec5af6e8053f66d08582646ae8c1c59ed5","tid":1395972,"uid":79563,